*                JOINTimedNodeStage DTO.
*  
*               This DAO should be used as a central point for the mapping between 
*                the JOINTimedNodeStage DTO and a SQL database.
*
* Link:         http://balusc.blogspot.com/2008/07/dao-tutorial-data-layer.html
